    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的继任者将如何应对特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/how-trudeau-s-successor-will-handle-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼和克里斯蒂娅·弗里兰是接替即将卸任的加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的热门人选。Oyster Group 合伙人阿曼达·加尔布雷斯和加拿大亚太基金会副总裁维娜·纳吉布拉在彭博社的“与哈斯琳达·阿明的洞察”节目中谈到了他们认为加拿大下一任领导人将如何应对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的回归。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/how-trudeau-s-successor-will-handle-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 06:05:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025 年起海运价格将因关税上涨和罢工担忧而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/shipping-rates-start-2025-with-a-spike-on-tariff-strike-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一个月，从亚洲向美国运送货物的现货集装箱运费大幅上涨，原因是各家公司都希望在罢工前避免更高的关税，并补充库存。罢工可能导致美国大约一半的海运贸易量港口关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/shipping-rates-start-2025-with-a-spike-on-tariff-strike-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 06:04:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港融资成本飙升 人民币做空者受压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港人民币融资成本飙升至多年未见的水平，表明人们担心北京方面稳定人民币的努力可能会导致离岸市场流动性收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/offshore-yuan-borrowing-costs-surge-as-currency-support-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nickel Asia 计划向住友出售加工厂股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nickel-asia-aims-to-sell-processing-plant-stake-to-sumitomo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最大的镍生产商亚洲镍业公司 (Nickel Asia Corp.) 正就将其在一家重要加工厂的少数股权出售给日本住友金属矿业公司进行谈判，因为这家公司专注于上游采矿和可再生能源业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/nickel-asia-aims-to-sell-processing-plant-stake-to-sumitomo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>APS 称腾讯股价下跌带来买入机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/tencent-share-dip-presents-buying-opportunity-aps-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位基金经理在上个季度的表现优于 90% 的同行，他表示，尽管腾讯被列入美国国防部黑名单，但他仍然看好其商业模式。APS Asset Management 创始人兼联席首席投资官王国辉 (Wong Kok Hoi) 还讨论了他持有的顶级股票，包括中芯国际，以及对中国刺激计划的预期。他在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与 David Ingles 和 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/tencent-share-dip-presents-buying-opportunity-aps-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治因素颠覆赌注，货币期权交易飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/currency-options-trading-is-skyrocketing-as-politics-upend-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，规模逾 3,000 亿美元的货币期权市场一开始平静无波，但政治新闻引发了近两个月来最繁忙的交易日 — — 这预示着 2025 年的形势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/currency-options-trading-is-skyrocketing-as-politics-upend-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 05:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元因定盘价和散户投资者流入而跌至 7 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yen-weakens-to-lowest-since-july-on-fixing-retail-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率跌至七月以来的最低水平，表现不及所有主要货币，分析师将日元下跌归因于日本散户投资者的资金流出以及东京基准汇率的调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/yen-weakens-to-lowest-since-july-on-fixing-retail-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 04:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
